{
    "title": "Pra Machucar Meu Coração",
    "artist": "Edu Lobo",
    "lyricsHtml": "\nIntro: <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bdim7\">Bdim7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bbmaj7\">Bbmaj7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7(9)\">Gm7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Está fazendo um ano e meio, amor</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm7\">Cm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que o nosso lar      desmoronou</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(9)\">F7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bbmaj7\">Bbmaj7</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7\">Eb7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6/E\">Gm6/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Meu sabiá,        meu violão</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E uma cruel desilusão</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Foi tudo que ficou</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#dim7\">G#dim7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Fi     - cou</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(9)\">C7(9)</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7(b9)\">C7(b9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Prá machucar meu coração</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7(9)\">Gm7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Está fazendo um ano e meio, amor</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm7\">Cm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que o nosso lar      desmoronou</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(9)\">F7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bbmaj7\">Bbmaj7</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7\">Eb7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6/E\">Gm6/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Meu sabiá,        meu violão</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E uma cruel desilusão</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Foi tudo que ficou</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#dim7\">G#dim7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Fi     - cou</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#dim7\">G#dim7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Prá machucar meu coração</span>\n\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Quem sabe, não foi bem melhor assim</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7(6)\">A7(6)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Melhor prá você e melhor prá mim</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A vida é uma escola</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Onde a gente precisa aprender</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">A ciência de viver prá não sofrer</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7\">Dm7</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7(9)\">Gm7(9)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Está fazendo um ano e meio, amor</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6\">Gm6</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm7\">Cm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que o nosso lar      desmoronou</span>\n     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F7(9)\">F7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bbmaj7\">Bbmaj7</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Eb7\">Eb7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm6/E\">Gm6/E</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Meu sabiá,        meu violão</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E uma cruel desilusão</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am7\">Am7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Foi tudo que ficou</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#dim7\">G#dim7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Gm7\">Gm7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Fi     - cou</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fmaj7\">Fmaj7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Prá machucar meu coração</span>\n",
